        "Instructions": "['Toss cucumbers in a large bowl with vinegar, sugar, red pepper flakes, and 2 tsp. salt. Chill, tossing once, at least 1 hour and up to 6 hours.', 'Just before serving, add dill and lemon juice and toss to combine. Taste and season with more salt if needed.']",
